body.name: Flying Glider Plane - 24 Pack (8") Small Model Aircrafts in Assorted Designs. Each Comes in Colorful Envelope. Great Party Favor, Carnival Prizes (24 Piece)
features: Introducing our Flying Glider Plane – a thrilling 8" small model aircraft that promises hours of airborne excitement. This set features assorted designs, each carefully crafted for optimal aerodynamics and performance. Packaged in colorful envelopes, these gliders make for a delightful surprise and a fantastic party favor or carnival prize.😃😃😃

Watch as these miniature planes take flight with ease, captivating the imagination of both children and adults. These Planes Soar Through The Air With Its Propellers Spinning At High Speed. The assorted designs add an element of fun and anticipation, making each glider a unique and exciting experience.✈️✈️✈️

Perfect for parties, events, or as carnival prizes, these Flying Glider Planes offer a blend of entertainment and nostalgia. Simply assemble and launch them into the air for a thrilling aerobatic display. The compact size makes them easy to carry and share, ensuring that the joy of flight can be experienced by everyone.🛫🛫🛫

Add a touch of whimsy and adventure to your next gathering with these Flying Glider Planes. Whether you're planning a birthday party, a carnival, or simply want to surprise your little aviators, these small model aircrafts are sure to soar to new heights of fun!🛩️🛩️🛩️
24 Pack. Easy to Assemble. Size 8". Made Of Sturdy Styrofoam. Individually Packaged - Each Glider Comes in Colorful Envelope. For Ages 3+. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
